Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去喊少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是客人客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您除了客人就不想些別的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份工作就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出暗訪記者  並給予重點服務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後成功進入排行榜前列
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是讓我幫忙  我也什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼忙都幫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧客都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情應該是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停靠在9號月台  14時15分  開往森田的列車很快就要發車了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場宴會差不多也要到高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是由新娘的朋友們給我們帶來的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  有請
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  個子差不多高到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後頭髮也理得亂糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天大概不是亂糟糟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請讓我看一下名冊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這實在是有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給椿之間的客人們上過茶點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我請你們去拿一套大號浴袍來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是非常抱歉  我們馬上就去拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我這就去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茶點就拜託你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是緒花？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她問會場的房間也好什麼也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她問這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只記得說是同級生的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  謝謝你  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生  蔬菜我切好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  緒花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是同級生的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他更詳細的情況就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去就找不到徹先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那個  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法回你簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙的樣子  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事…貌似這次還真有事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就為了去找徹先生跑了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連要怎麼找他都沒有考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算找到了徹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的事情也不知道能不能順利搞定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會順利的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  你以前有過好好考慮完才行動的先例嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不都想辦法克服困難一路走來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花你要是覺得那是最好的辦法而去做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會船到橋頭自然直的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後也一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  一定會船到橋頭自然直的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…  要是我真幫到你了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害哦  阿孝果然好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能正好在我最消沉的時候打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  你找我有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…其實也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花  你現在在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.96,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在會場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  會場又是在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我到市裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近的旅館果然好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去市裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  咦  阿孝你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像聽到些什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝總是好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是會來鼓勵我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們隔得那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…我其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝都來為我鼓勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能繼續消沉下去呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我絕對會把徹先生給找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功戰勝此次危機！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  要戰勝它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是可能的話連我的份也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀  阿孝也要戰勝它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有什麼危機出現了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  話說菜子負責的桐之間裡的小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得他以前好像也來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我還沒在這裡工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  小野寺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  還真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這本記事本是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著他的女兒討厭吃魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去告知一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記事本…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  我可以問一下新郎的年齡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  可以告知我新郎的年齡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名冊就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要新郎的年齡就好  請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全多虧了阿…孝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在阿孝的面子上  請和我一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你的意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  回市裡的班次是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要等四十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你謝謝你謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒什麼誒啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的跟你道多少聲謝都不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到徹先生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.47,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  全都多虧了阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你又在搞什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去…去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去…去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真是的  當然是喜翠莊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的工作才是關鍵 必須拿出幹勁才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  亂成一團真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再跟你發簡訊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  這裡是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備給月之間的客人進行按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Time is money對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  波之間的客人晚餐時間由你作陪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不湊巧  本館今天已經客滿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭盔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停車場的管理員借給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…心想著把徹先生帶回去一定會有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難得出席朋友的婚禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼強硬地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那是最佳選擇所以才來找我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼信任我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會搞定給你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來  要出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生說的話好像之前也聽誰說過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹先生  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點稍大的頭盔中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種第一次聞到的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生腦袋的氣味是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝的腦袋也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽小民說  蓮先生有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平時有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮岸徹我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  趕快進入工作狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼找到徹先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解釋的話就說來話長了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡你應該說「沒關係  告訴我吧」吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生  讓民子來負責油炸可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去炸天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止你都在學些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候  我好像聽到有什麼開始運作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派上用處了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我自己也有做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  不要為這種小事大驚小怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…巴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顧客都是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情應該是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是喜翠莊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.71,0:16:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（註：松、竹、梅為料理等級，松為特上等、竹為上等、梅為普通）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫錯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是本旅館的特別料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特別的上等料理…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好放鬆休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓮先生  這邊完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  雕刻就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六…七…八…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.09,0:17:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油聲變了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請嘗嘗沙丁魚的天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:17:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的油聲  記住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺好溫暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些溫啊  不過作為第一次的料理 這已經很不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  你指的是食物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你來這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了來拿天婦羅呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著  馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人您滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.45,0:18:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們總算結束了老闆娘不在的漫長的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.57,0:19:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月之間的顧客要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那兩位是暗訪記者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能取得好分數了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰是都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經盡力招待了所有顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是分數才是重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  緒花  還有工作要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李就這些了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你哦  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你幫忙做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝  您有好好休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.63,0:20:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  昨天女兒突然說要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太匆忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是工作無論如何都要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.01,0:20:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這個不能說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.76,0:20:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽很好的休息過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一身輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.97,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰是記者一點都沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招待的心情應該是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以能這麼努力多虧了阿孝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝一君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天到貨的新作…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看到我就虛脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.64,0:21:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分  虧我那麼拼命地找
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味呢  這個天婦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.01,0:23:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  不是的  緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}你一個人不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}回來吧  緒花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠莊也不會有事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
